rows.label: qst100306_msg0002
rows.name:
Old friend who give Pupun tasty food,
and took care of Vacuum Brogs! ...And
got parts for repair...hehe...

rows.label: qst100306_msg0003
rows.name:
Thanks to friends'...constant...support,
Pupun complete full 40 hours of
flight training!

rows.label: qst100306_msg0004
rows.name:
Pupun got license with
big rubber stamp. Now
fully-fledged Nopon pilot!

rows.label: qst100306_msg0006
rows.name:
Friend want thank-you for tasty
treats? And money for parts?

rows.label: qst100306_msg0007
rows.name:
Ah, actually... Pupun not
begin career quite yet... A
bit broke... Training fees...

rows.label: qst100306_msg0008
rows.name:
Oh, but this terrible! Pupun
have sudden feeling that flying
skills are fading away!

rows.label: qst100306_msg0009
rows.name:
Pupun lose skills if not
make regular flights...

rows.label: qst100306_msg0010
rows.name:
Yes, Pupun must go off flying
again right now. So, byeeeee!
